{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"279e954c95","title":"关于派军队干部训练学校师生的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"71d868025a","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"279e954c95"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3be4d5766f","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"94b47e3473","type":"title","text":"关于派军队干部训练学校师生的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"279e954c95"},{"id":"c4703540e7","type":"paragraph","text":"派军队干部训练革命师生的方法很好。训练一下和不训练大不一样。这样做，可以向解放军学政治，学军事，学四个第一，学三八作风，学三大纪律八项注意，加强组织纪律性。驻京部队派干部训练革命师生的经验很好，很有成效，应当在全国推广。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"279e954c95"}],"page":{"id":"551616cee2","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"279e954c95","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}